  "prompt": "Where can I get very professional fire inspection service in Sydney?",
  "response": "For professional fire inspection services in Sydney, you can consider reaching out to licensed and reputable companies that specialize in fire safety compliance and inspection services. Some options include:\n\n1. **Wormald** - A well-known company offering comprehensive fire protection services, including inspections and compliance checks.\n\n2. **Chubb** - Provides fire safety solutions and inspection services for various types of buildings.\n\n3. **FireSafe ANZ** - Specializes in fire protection and offers inspection, testing, and compliance certification.\n\n4. **Aegis Safe** - Offers a range of fire safety services, including inspections and building certification.\n\n5. **Australian Fire Services** - Provides fire inspection and compliance services tailored to meet Australian standards.\n\n6. **VIP Fire & Safety** - Offers inspections, maintenance, and compliance checks for fire safety systems.\n\nWhen selecting a service provider, ensure they are certified with relevant regulatory bodies and have a good track record in the industry. You can also check customer reviews and request quotes to compare services and pricing.",
